texts.text: The End City Ship can be found near the End City Tower which contains an elytra and few loot chests.
In Java the path to load the structure from a structure block is minecraft:end_city/ship.

1 Dimensions
2 Materials
3 Block orientation and instructions
4 Blueprints
The end ship is 24 blocks high, 29 blocks long and 13 blocks wide.
